8 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Transfer of funds. (1) By June 30, 2025, the state treasurer shall
9 transfer $50 million from the general fund to the local disaster resiliency fund provided for in 17-7-133, MCA.
10 (2) During the biennium ending June 30, 2027, the state treasurer shall transfer $50 million from
11 the general fund to the local disaster resiliency fund provided for in 17-7-133, MCA.
12
13 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Effective date. [This act] is effective on passage and approval.
